text: Csaba Ali (4 November 1946 - 27 December 2020) was a Hungarian swimmer. He competed in two events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. He was born in Eger, Hungary. Ali died on 27 December 2020 at the age of 74.Elhunyt az egykori kiváló úszó, Ali Csaba ==References== Category:1946 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Olympians for Hungary Category:Hungarian swimmers Category:Heves County
